# Trivy vulnerability ignore file
# Format: one CVE-ID or GHSA-ID per line, optionally followed by an expiry date
# Example:
#   CVE-2023-12345
#   GHSA-xxxx-yyyy-zzzz until:2026-06-01
#
# Add entries here for accepted risks or vulnerabilities with no available fix
# when ignore-unfixed: true in the workflow does not cover them.

# ncurses: heap-based buffer overflow in _nc_captoinfo (captoinfo.c) that may
# lead to arbitrary code execution via crafted input. Unfixed in Debian Bookworm
# (python:3.13-slim base). apt-get upgrade -y will apply the fix automatically
# once Debian releases a patched package. Revisit at expiry.
CVE-2021-39537 until:2026-10-01
